# Quality Gates — Thresholds per Deliverable

## Gate Flow
IDLE → RESEARCH → BRIEFING → PRODUCTION → DELIVERED
Each transition requires validate_gate.

## Thresholds

### VSL
- blind_critic >= 8 (per chapter)
- emotional_stress_test genericidade >= 8
- black_validation >= 8/10
- Human approves MUP before production

### Landing Page
- blind_critic >= 8 (per block)
- emotional_stress_test genericidade >= 8
- black_validation >= 8/10

### Creative
- blind_critic >= 8
- emotional_stress_test genericidade >= 8
- black_validation >= 8/10

### MUP/MUS
- consensus: multi-model agreement
- blind_critic >= 8 (MUP + MUS statements)
- emotional_stress_test genericidade >= 8
- voc_search: quotes found
- HUMAN approval (mandatory)

### Email Sequence
- blind_critic >= 8 (per email)
- emotional_stress_test genericidade >= 8
- black_validation >= 8/10

## Mandatory Tools per Gate
| Gate | Mandatory | Alternatives |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| Research | firecrawl_agent, voc_search | firecrawl_scrape, playwright |
| Briefing | get_phase_context | — |
| Production | blind_critic, emotional_stress_test | — |

## Path-Based Blocking
| Write to | Precondition |
|----------|-------------|
| research/ | None |
| briefings/ | gates.research = true |
| production/ | gates.briefing = true AND mecanismo VALIDATED/APPROVED |
